<bug>
	<id>154</id>
	<title>Media: Creating a post from media page creates a "ghost" media item and breaks UI</title>
	<description>
		<paragraph id="1">
			<sentence id="1.1">To reproduce: 
On the media list, long press to enter selection mode.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.2">Select a single item and tap the post button.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.3">Edit the post and publish.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.4">You're back on the media list, notice that there is an extra copy of the item at the bottom of the list.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.5">Rotate to change orientation.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.6">Notice that the thumbnails for both the original and the extra copy are missing, as well as the dimensions.</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="2">
			<sentence id="2.1">Nexus 7 / 2.5 beta 3</sentence>
		</paragraph>
	</description>
</bug>
